1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,220
This man has your father's body but he's not Chino.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:05,400
His name is Jacobo Reyes.

3
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:08,900
- How do you know that?
- Because he told me.

4
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:13,860
He came to bring me the things that Mrs. Silvina sent us when we moved here.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:17,080
We were both surprised.

6
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:19,780
It's just that-- It's just, no--

7
00:00:19,780 --> 00:00:21,500
None of these things you're telling me make sense.

8
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:26,280
No, it didn't make sense to me either. He had to try really hard to convince me that he wasn't your father.

9
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,500
And why didn't you tell me?

10
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:33,160
Because he asked me not to. He said that if I told you, it could complicate things.

11
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:34,880
It's just that--

12
00:00:35,260 --> 00:00:37,760
And if he's not Chino, then who is he?

13
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:39,800
I already told you.

14
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:42,440
His name is Jacobo Reyes, that's all I know.

15
00:00:44,540 --> 00:00:46,880
But he was very nice to me and

16
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:50,720
I want to keep the promise of not revealing his secret.

17
00:00:51,140 --> 00:00:52,280
What--?

18
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:56,540
Not revealing the secret that he is not Chino Valdes?

19
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,880
He's a hitman, mom.

20
00:00:59,220 --> 00:01:03,700
Chino is very clever, he can make up any excuse to get into that house and do whatever he was asked to do.

21
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:06,440
But he is not your father.

22
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,060
Why would I lie to you?

23
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,440
No, not you. Him!

24
00:01:11,420 --> 00:01:12,940
Please, Juliana.

25
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:17,380
Don't tell Valentina that her driver lives in your father's body.

26
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:20,760
Of course I'm not gonna tell her. She'll think I'm crazy.

27
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:22,120
Please.

28
00:01:22,880 --> 00:00:00,000
Keep this secret.

